lead_paragraph: Pat Summitt, the winningest coach in U.S. Division I college basketball history, died on Tuesday at the age of 64, the University of Tennessee said.

headline.print_headline: Legendary U.S. Women's Basketball Coach Pat Summitt Dies at 64
